{"title":"Ari Bonneville e-Road Bike Speeds Up Off the Flats","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike/","date":1722519300000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-action-1-1536x1004.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1004\" alt=\"ari bonneville e-road bike being ridden fast.\" /></p>\n<p>Whether you want to set your own land speed records, crush more miles, or just keep up with your faster cycling buddies, the new Ari Bonneville e-road bike pairs a Fazua Ride 60 motor with a 430Wh battery for a lightweight assist up to 28mph.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2100\" height=\"1293\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1.jpg\" alt=\"ari bonneville e-road bike shown from side.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1.jpg 2100w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1-297x183.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1-1536x946.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1-120x74.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1-768x473.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-1-2048x1261.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s an endurance road bike, with a taller front end and sloping top tube for a lower center of gravity and good standover. That makes it comfortable for long rides…and more approachable for newbies.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1112\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"ari bonneville e-road bike shown from front and rear angles.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-297x129.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-1536x667.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-120x52.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-768x334.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-2-2048x890.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s also a performance road bike, with a lightweight carbon frame that has dropped seatstays both for compliance and to keep the rear end laterally stiff when you’re hammering. It has the handling and feel of a regular high-end road bike bike, just with a bit more <em>oomph</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2.jpg\" alt=\"closeup details of ari bonneville e-road bike.\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-details-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It fits up to 700×40 tires, and comes with a UDH derailleur hanger that’s “Full Mount” compatible in case you want to add a SRAM Transmission derailleur back there.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-geometry-chart-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1083\" height=\"553\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-geometry-chart-1.jpg\" alt=\"ari bonneville geometry chart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-geometry-chart-1.jpg 1083w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-geometry-chart-1-297x152.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-geometry-chart-1-120x61.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike-geometry-chart-1-768x392.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Complete bikes from $4,999 to $6,999, or build your own with the frameset for $4,499. Ari has a 30-day trial period for all new bikes, and a lifetime warranty on the frame and fork.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://aribikes.com/products/bonneville\" target=\"_blank\">AriBikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ari-bonneville-e-road-bike/\">Ari Bonneville e-Road Bike Speeds Up Off the Flats</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d98fbf00b7b3980b6cee69ac5ebfd3ddcfa3f496c630dc061fdd81adf8b8a0e6","category":"Cycling"}